    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2288070/extras/8e5a0b52b1ac4c82844d9e5255f9572b.poster.avif?t=1751266820\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2288070/extras/8e5a0b52b1ac4c82844d9e5255f9572b.webm?t=1751266820\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2288070/extras/8e5a0b52b1ac4c82844d9e5255f9572b.mp4?t=1751266820\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>街机游戏《NinjaWarriors》于 1987 年发布，以其流畅的格斗动作和与无数敌人的殊死搏斗风靡全球。1994年推出了SFC版《The NinjaWarriors Again》，在原作的基础上加入了新角色和许多新boss。 本作是以该 SFC 版为基础，时隔 25 年集结当时的开发主力“TENGO PROJECT”成员完成的复刻版。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2288070/extras/6513454e72b4282e0d268983121d95f8.avif?t=1751266820\" width=600 height=350 /></span><br>在STEAM版中，日文版游戏名称《<strong>The NinjaWarriors Once Again</strong>》将更改为全球版游戏名称《<strong>The Ninja Saviors: Return of the Warriors</strong>》，日文版与全球版将以同一应用软体在全球发售。 本游戏能够与世界各地的玩家竞争以解锁成就和排行榜！<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2288070/extras/58c26d071acd853540992f08e600cc62.poster.avif?t=1751266820\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2288070/extras/58c26d071acd853540992f08e600cc62.webm?t=1751266820\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2288070/extras/58c26d071acd853540992f08e600cc62.mp4?t=1751266820\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>在保留 16 位原游戏风格的同时，角色分辨率和模式数量等，配合最新的硬件大幅升级！<br>另外，让玩家能够体验到新鲜的格斗动作风格，添加了两个新角色。 在攻略进行后能解锁该角色。<br>同时新增加了前作中未能实现的两人合作游玩模式！<br>通关后，还能挑战每个关卡的时间竞速模式！ 让玩家能够以成为最快的忍者为目标，充分享受游戏。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2288070/extras/f21864c8a2ce02eaf8c3a3044a7d5f16.poster.avif?t=1751266820\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2288070/extras/f21864c8a2ce02eaf8c3a3044a7d5f16.webm?t=1751266820\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2288070/extras/f21864c8a2ce02eaf8c3a3044a7d5f16.mp4?t=1751266820\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >关于 TENGO PROJECT</h2>隶属于NatsumeAtari Co., Ltd.的特别开发团队，至今为时开发了数十款高性能的动作的游戏。 团队从红白机时代就开始制作家用游戏，由现在任然活跃于第一线的三名开发人员组成。 除了本作之外，<strong>Pocky &amp; Rocky Reshrined</strong>、<strong>WILD GUNS Reloaded</strong> 等游戏也在 STEAM 发行。",
